Nigerian singer, Mr Eazi is not resting with making bangers and his song, “Surrender” which is off his recently released Lagos to London album is a jam to listen to. The singer in the visual for the song which has vocals from the songbird, Simi employs the use of animated imagery as he sings about his love for a woman. Unable to resist, he croons about surrounding to the waist bead of his love interest whose animated character can be seen gyrating her hips in tune to his lyrics. Simi’s lyrics give the song a balance as she gently also sings about her surrender to a man whom she is unable to resist due to his charm. This is a playful song that will surely appeal to every romantic and sensual bone in your body without being overly sexual. Watch the video below: 